title: Hawkwind - Kings of Speed, Lords of Light FLAC
description:
Kings of Speed, Lords of Light
------------------------------

Ripped from CD using EAC & converted to FLAC.

Allegedly 18/5/91 at "Latin Quarter, Detroit", but actually recorded at the Zeche in Bochum, Germany 8/10/91.  Crew are of course Dave Brock, Alan Davey, and Richard Chadwick.  

78 minutes of excellent audience recording and the cover's not bad, though of course not from this gig or tour (looks like Harvey on the front, and that's Huw on the back). Timing's from the tracks, not the CD cover.

Needle Gun (5.11)
Ejection/Time We Left (9.03)
Blue Shift/The Right Stuff (12.26)
Snake Dance/Night of the Hawks (10.32)
Levitation (12.23)
Master of the Universe (5.42)
The Golden Void (7.00)
Paranoia/Hassan I Sahba (7.17)
LSD (9.08)

Enjoy
